n combination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/96044/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, More', 'Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Esomeprazole, Glucosamine, Tolazoline, Dimethyl sulfoxide', 1767369485);
